title: Trendzo Gracie 9/13: Robert Sarver, CPI, GoldenEye, Tom Brady, Redeem Team, Minnesota, Emmy's
itunes:title: Trendzo Gracie 9/13: Robert Sarver, CPI, GoldenEye, Tom Brady, Redeem Team, Minnesota, Emmy's
description:
In this edition of Trendzo Gracie, Jack and Miles discuss Robert Sarver getting suspended from the NBA for being a POS, Wall Street's worst day since June 2020, the re-release of 'GoldenEye 007', Gisele Bundchen's reaction to Tom Brady's un-retirement, Netflix' 'Redeem Team' trailer,  Minnesota accidentally legalizing THC, and the Emmy's... occuring!
